original: Bäckner, Johan August, kyrkoherde, kontraktsprost. Ed, f. 19/10/91 d Färge-1’anda, Älvsb. — Stud:’ex. i Vänensb. 12, teol. fil. €x. 13, teol. kand., prakt, teol. prov samt prästv. f. Karlstads -stift 17. Tjg. IS. v. pastor i Norra Råda, Siillerud o. Köla, kommin. i Töftedal 20, kyrkoh. i Rämen 29, i Dals-Ed &td. 39. Kontr :pro’St. öv. Västra Dals kontr. 47.
translated: Bäckner, Johan August, parish priest, dean. Born October 19, 1891 in Färge-1’anda, Älvsborg county. He passed studentexamen in Vänensb. in 1912, teol. fil. exam in 1913, teol. kand. exam, practical theological examination and became a priest in Karlstads diocese in 1917. He served as temporary vicar in Norra Råda, Siillerud, and Köla, assistant vicar in Töftedal in 1920, vicar in Rämen in 1929, and in Dals-Ed in 1939. He became Dean over the Western Dals deanery in 1947. Note that '\d\d m. partners name' means that the person married in the year 19xx.
